local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["bungalow"]={"bungalow","['bʌŋgələʊ]","[ˈbʌŋɡəˌlo]","n.(有凉台的)平房",'n.(有凉台的)平房,小屋','I\'d rather live in this old house with all its inconveniences than in one of those pokey bungalows where you haven\'t room to swing a cat.','尽管诸多不便，我宁愿住在这幢老房子里，也不愿住到那种狭小的平房里，在那里你连转身的地方都没有。','His country cottage turned out to be an enormous bungalow.','他的“乡下房子”原来是一座大平房。'}
